      "version": "1.4.0",
      "status": "verified",
      "text": "Name: Release Readiness Radar\nDescription: Checks a service for release blockers across CI status, changelog coverage, environment config, and rollback readiness.\nOrganization: SEL-Core\nStatus: verified\nVersion: 1.4.0\nTechnologies: GitHub Actions, Node.js, YAML\nPrimary specialization: release_engineering\nDomain specific: CI Governance, Deployment Safety, Rollback Planning\nTasks: Check Release Gates - Validates CI checks, environment readiness, and required approvals before release.\nDocumentation: https://github.com/sel/platform/blob/main/release-radar/README.md https://github.com/sel/platform/blob/main/release-radar/README.md#usage v1.4 adds rollback verification and release gate scoring",
